sequenceDiagram
    participant SatEngine as Saturation Engine
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>(Thanos Querier)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Cache as Decision Cache<br/>(In-memory)
    participant VACtrl as VA Controller
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Actuator as Actuator<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PromServer as Prometheus Server<br/>(ServiceMonitor)
    participant HPA as HPA / KEDA

    Note over SatEngine,HPA: Flow 1: Saturation-Based Autoscaling Decision
    SatEngine->>Prometheus: PromQL query (KV cache, queue depth)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token (SA)
    Prometheus-->>SatEngine: Metrics response
    SatEngine->>Cache: Store scaling decision<br/>(in-process)
    Cache->>VACtrl: Trigger reconciliation<br/>(Go channel)
    VACtrl->>K8sAPI: Update VariantAutoscaling status<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>VACtrl: Status updated
    SatEngine->>Actuator: Register metrics<br/>(in-process)

    Note over PromServer,HPA: Flow 2: Metrics Scraping by External Autoscaler
    PromServer->>Actuator: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS, Bearer Token (SA)
    Actuator-->>PromServer: wva_desired_replicas, wva_desired_ratio
    HPA->>PromServer: Query WVA metrics<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token
    PromServer-->>HPA: Scaling metrics
    HPA->>K8sAPI: Scale Deployment (scale subresource)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token

    Note over SatEngine,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Scale-from-Zero
    participant SFZEngine as Scale-from-Zero Engine
    SFZEngine->>Prometheus: Query request count<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token (SA)
    Prometheus-->>SFZEngine: Request metrics
    SFZEngine->>K8sAPI: Scale Deployment (0 -> N)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token (SA)

    Note over VACtrl,K8sAPI: Flow 4: InferencePool Tracking
    participant IPCtrl as InferencePool Controller
    participant DS as Datastore (In-memory)
    IPCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool CRs<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>IPCtrl: InferencePool events
    IPCtrl->>DS: Update endpoint pool<br/>(in-process)
